VIII Mobile VAS Conference (November 24-25, St. Petersburg, www.vasforum.ru). 
This year we will discuss the following key topics: 
- Russian & global mobile content market trends (with a special focus on China market); 
- Mobile application (marketplaces, marketing, monetization, games & entertainment apps); 
- Mobile carrier strategies in changing VAS ecosystem; 
- New mobile devices, platforms and their opportunities (for developers, content providers, carriers); 
- Mobile Internet and social networks; 
- New ideas and start-ups. 
Among speakers: 
- Nadezhda Antsiferova, Chairman, Mobile Content & Service Provider Association; 
- Alexey Kireev, Products and New Business Development Director, Kyivstar; 
- Denis Nochevnov, New Technologies & Services Director, MegaFon; 
- Kirill Petrov, Managing Director, i-Free Innovations; 
- Pavel Roitberg, Internet Services Development Director, MTS; 
- Ralph Simon, Chairman Emeritus & Founder, MEF - Americas; 
- Olga Steidl, Vice President, SPB Software; 
- Peter Vesterbacka, "Mighty Eagle," Rovio Mobile.
